Dia. 01 Taking own Liberty
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Hopefully nobody thinks that it is possible to capture Black with White 1.
\par This move creates shortage of liberties.
\par
\par After Black's hane at 2, White is captured.
\par It is not possible to play at A, right?
\par
\par }
