Dia. 02 Pae
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Connecting at 1 is too calm.
\par Sometimes it is good just filling the liberties, but not in this situation.
\par
\par Black's attachment at 1 is a great move.
\par After White 3, Black can resist and make pae with 4.
\par \cf1\b Pae is a failure\cf0\b0  for White.
\par
\par
\par }
