Dia. 03 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White's \cf1\b diagonal attachment\cf0\b0  at 1 is the\cf1\b  vital point of this capturing race\cf0\b0 .
\par Black has no choice but to play the hane at 2, but then if White connects at 3 he wins the capturing race.
\par
\par Black has shortage of liberties so he can't play dansu at A.
\par
\par
\par }
